{"tid":217440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"資本主義本身好大問題，有錢人越有錢，窮人起窮","createTime":"2017-04-25T18:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T18:04:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e749c187b55e4858c5048af268588e7c217dd7","tid":217440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T18:44:22.000Z","msg":"人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無"},{"pid":"ece353ff7e6dc510af58662786797a77299a1866","tid":217440,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T18:49:13.000Z","msg":"資本主義最勁既地方係令奴隸甘受壓迫<br />\n就好似連登仔咁<br />\n專捧減有錢佬稅,向窮人緊縮社會保障既右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8e240618a7205122bcc56acd85beb2b7c42b70","tid":217440,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T18:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n收重稅嗰啲叫社會主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20eac0a969f308755e209cebc312c55dd85ea726","tid":217440,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n收重稅嗰啲叫社會主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國先進國家大把係咁，呢啲唔係社會主義"},{"pid":"b438b38e7b3f6d1163fedee6541021aaa2082076","tid":217440,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:03:51.000Z","msg":"睇你點睇咩係「重稅」啦<br />\n40幾50%根本好多國家都係<br />\n人地一樣貧富懸殊，英國就係噉"},{"pid":"d31ab99e73608f2940e796c7ed9b88296d766bc6","tid":217440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你點睇咩係「重稅」啦<br />\n40幾50%根本好多國家都係<br />\n人地一樣貧富懸殊，英國就係噉</blockquote><br />\n所以咪姐係資本主義有問題囉，就算重稅都係資本主義"},{"pid":"95a027245f2397d68518205c50630dc23e113f65","tid":217440,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你點睇咩係「重稅」啦<br />\n40幾50%根本好多國家都係<br />\n人地一樣貧富懸殊，英國就係噉</blockquote><br />\n所以咪姐係資本主義有問題囉，就算重稅都係資本主義</blockquote><br />\n有錢佬太多手段啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終有一日會仆獲甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過可能我地死左都未見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d863d6214df166498abb3eeda58a88a97335b981","tid":217440,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:22:10.000Z","msg":"係啊好大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令到當時馬列毛主義咁易入侵半個世界"},{"pid":"c35e894081e7266a189049a4f457a8f0aea32cdb","tid":217440,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你點睇咩係「重稅」啦<br />\n40幾50%根本好多國家都係<br />\n人地一樣貧富懸殊，英國就係噉</blockquote><br />\n所以咪姐係資本主義有問題囉，就算重稅都係資本主義</blockquote><br />\n重稅唔係劃一咁收架嘛<br />\n窮人又收一半 有錢人又收一半<br />\n咪冇咗重新分配社會資源嘅意義<br />\n同埋稅制可以針對返有錢人<br />\n例如遺產稅 利得稅<br />\n咁咪可以避免向窮人開刀"},{"pid":"8eedc3ca3b79687928d8dcfb4ff57de31c93c8ef","tid":217440,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:45:12.000Z","msg":"中間路綫社會民主主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bcd4cb8f73c081808291373ac8fb3ee0b9313d","tid":217440,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n收重稅嗰啲叫社會主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國先進國家大把係咁，呢啲唔係社會主義</blockquote><br />\n得北歐係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議你讀多啲有關社會政策研究嘅書"},{"pid":"69deb95983db63b9e6107897704170d9f94303fb","tid":217440,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"無民主既資本主義先係最大問題<br />\n你睇下香港，中國"},{"pid":"19a40c95e77da56e1ef6cf97cc02c0e25808d1bf","tid":217440,"uid":35682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n所以中國某d朝代直接將商人地位排落最低都唔係無原因<br />\n商人勢力做大會影響政治"},{"pid":"be08c8ff011c9443aedd872173da065010da0091","tid":217440,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n收重稅嗰啲叫社會主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國先進國家大把係咁，呢啲唔係社會主義</blockquote><br />\n社會民主主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e5ae1470a60e78cbc983e5adf3c8accc4b5408","tid":217440,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:20:14.000Z","msg":"有錢佬玩財技 稅呢樣野根本唔係問題"},{"pid":"6ba5720fce4bc73643c11617dc1992eefb308b77","tid":217440,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:21:11.000Z","msg":"香港=資本家天堂"},{"pid":"b891cb20349e5263acddfaf1998b721f030484db","tid":217440,"uid":11078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:23:35.000Z","msg":"所以咪會有無產階級革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7523080ef6585df1d874c0bc3bd79a0f6757138f","tid":217440,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:26:32.000Z","msg":"所以冇民主會有錢分？"},{"pid":"1f231638e547d2c654ff6e713e4aee36e58166e9","tid":217440,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:33:33.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"d972dcb356c270de224c6d535a98ce965db791ff","tid":217440,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n所以中國某d朝代直接將商人地位排落最低都唔係無原因<br />\n商人勢力做大會影響政治</blockquote><br />\n都唔係某啲特定朝代㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n商係末業根本係傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a267cb30237a3b8da96d0684215fe3745f2504","tid":217440,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以冇民主會有錢分？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有民主先有錢分<br />\n無民主=一小班商家佬玩哂"},{"pid":"f5315515c89f93f906cc28f175260feb836ecb9d","tid":217440,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"最大問題係當資本去到一個位<br />\n個持有者不事生產但獲得既資源都俾生產既人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0055847ee15773833af5f14d27222f43c69966d","tid":217440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b186d357747fa7d40ab2853006af40a343d61e6","tid":217440,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>資本主義最勁既地方係令奴隸甘受壓迫<br />\n就好似連登仔咁<br />\n專捧減有錢佬稅,向窮人緊縮社會保障既右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇計，佢地就係天生奴才命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1ea5c1e682b8554a1498f6ab6340d257eacd1a","tid":217440,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>資本主義最勁既地方係令奴隸甘受壓迫<br />\n就好似連登仔咁<br />\n專捧減有錢佬稅,向窮人緊縮社會保障既右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，呢點真係資本主義最勁既地方。<br />\n<br />\n奴隸係會資本家屌其他奴隸唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11be02d38d45501c4f0f3a67e5122e04ade7ec8","tid":217440,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最大問題係當資本去到一個位<br />\n個持有者不事生產但獲得既資源都俾生產既人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪股票同地產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1e8bfd1cb6acbe8787d305f9dd383cd0983a35","tid":217440,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"&quot;私有產權&quot;太深入民心啦, 根本無人懷疑過"},{"pid":"f22743acb6cdbeb034f008d8d095c75df47ee256","tid":217440,"uid":101433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:40:27.000Z","msg":"咁究竟用咩主義先最公平，最好"},{"pid":"95fc639f0741f9eb2ce77657c72a682064fa1eff","tid":217440,"uid":17813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以咪會有無產階級革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人淨係識唱今天我,又點會爆發到無產階級革命啊"},{"pid":"050721a7c2f5abaf24ee2f57cd92a504c7c6f318","tid":217440,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁究竟用咩主義先最公平，最好</blockquote><br />\n共產主義,不過依家嘅人無可能做得到,未來就得"},{"pid":"b9dd00455a5f905b674f8c4c7319ffa5614c1c7c","tid":217440,"uid":42460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"扮資本主義先係最大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 政府由中立 輔助市場發展嘅角色變成政策傾斜到有錢人或大機構<br />\n2. 市民制衡政府嘅能力有限<br />\n3. 加埋好多愚民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840cdfae7b0ecac4e319b0c24461c4f2cdfaffb1","tid":217440,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁究竟用咩主義先最公平，最好</blockquote><br />\n共產主義,不過依家嘅人無可能做得到,未來就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果純講理想，其實咩尻主義都可以係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6b988bca9bf675d30a82eb2b1efdc3c9093a4e","tid":217440,"uid":88544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁究竟用咩主義先最公平，最好</blockquote><br />\n共產主義,不過依家嘅人無可能做得到,未來就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果純講理想，其實咩尻主義都可以係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n齊來回歸享樂主義"},{"pid":"10f69154616d7dd3367ac21c1a8ce145e72313a3","tid":217440,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"2017喇，仲有人會信共慘主義？<br />\n<br />\n講資本主義同重稅可以睇下呢本書<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kqv5r9ln\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkqv5r9ln&h=0fb59771&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33d19d9eda6e1c2b6c635466d7cdf46301f98a10","tid":217440,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"重稅只係福利主義，都係用資本主義邏輯運作<br />\n與社會主義的主要差異在於主要生產工具的私有產權<br />\n福利主義的生產工具是私有<br />\n社會主義的主要生產工具是由社會擁有"},{"pid":"4ca8cd8bf3b6de23a5ae1975ff5b6c06a27851bd","tid":217440,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n你提既資本主義問題真係重稅平衝到？ 另外外國有平衡下到？<br />\n隔離飯香既傻鳩就唔好討論啲無絕對答案既問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02d3a112336a306a4ef78c013d5f6437a65f641","tid":217440,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"咁咪行社會主義，慢慢變窮，窮到人食係lo on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4d61da9214261165c509db40d3fcd0546d6ff0","tid":217440,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁究竟用咩主義先最公平，最好</blockquote><br />\n資本主義已經係best of worst"},{"pid":"a53cc50b137c76a7f5807ac8453518244476f605","tid":217440,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁究竟用咩主義先最公平，最好</blockquote><br />\n資本主義已經係best of worst</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n北歐個模式係最好,但你要係白人先work,亞洲賤種唔恨得咁多"},{"pid":"691f8df8fdf81ce0f4885b8318eb8315456c2bc5","tid":217440,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無民主既資本主義先係最大問題<br />\n你睇下香港，中國</blockquote><br />\n其實民主可以點幫手，向窮人傾斜，然後違反資本主義原則？<br />\n無一個主義解決到所以先有唔同主張，根本烏托邦終點就無人做到或有人唔想做到，而最接近我覺得係馬克思。"},{"pid":"efbd8dce77e30bffc273f1c7f65dff71ed7ce278","tid":217440,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人哋外國都話有得收重稅平衡下，香港乜都無</blockquote><br />\n所以中國某d朝代直接將商人地位排落最低都唔係無原因<br />\n商人勢力做大會影響政治</blockquote><br />\n咩勢力大唔會影響政治？<br />\n政治係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗皇帝全部人都排第99？"},{"pid":"e182a4c3de1e2e0b1b9821aa1d8cca1bdd897c16","tid":217440,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮資本主義先係最大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 政府由中立 輔助市場發展嘅角色變成政策傾斜到有錢人或大機構<br />\n2. 市民制衡政府嘅能力有限<br />\n3. 加埋好多愚民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1, 其實資本主義唔由政府介入就會有好多社會問題，所以介入係必然結果，無得用佢介入方向差而講佢扮緊，如果係咁介入幫市民都可以話扮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2,3 關資本主義事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbec13dc933379fae594990fe4ecf617dc52544","tid":217440,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過世界資源係夠全部人用<br />\n<br />\n人根本唔使用